snippet.title: Slender New Hope - Official Trailer | LimeStudio
snippet.description:
Slender - New Hope
... is based on Slender: The Eight Pages, but with modern graphic, better AI, bigger forest & a scary environment.

Disclaimer:
This game is currently in Pre-Alpha state! So there could be some bugs or performance issues. 

-----------------------------
Download for free: https://limestudio.itch.io/slender-new-hope
